Question 1

What is the purpose of the following block?

terraform {
  required_providers {
    azurerm = {
      source = "hashicorp/azurerm"
      version = "=4.1.0"
    }
  }
}
A.

Downloads Azure CLI

B.

Specifies which Terraform version to install

C.

Specifies the Azure provider and version Terraform should use

D.

Creates an Azure Resource Group

✅ Answer: C

Explanation

The required_providers block tells Terraform

Which provider to download
Where it comes from
Which version to install

Terraform downloads the provider during

terraform init
