A.
Terraform copies the value from Azure Portal

B.
Terraform reads the value from tfstate

C.
Terraform uses resource references

D.
Terraform guesses the location

✅ Answer: C

Explanation

Terraform automatically creates dependencies using references.

azurerm_resource_group.myrg.location

means

Use the location attribute of the Resource Group.

Terraform knows the VNet depends on the Resource Group.

